title: Sidewall - Sample, Album of Authentic Reproductions of Famous Historical Wall Papers, 1946
title_raw: Album of Authentic Reproductions of Famous Historical Wall Papers
description: Book, which has been unbound, contains 162 lengths of wallpapers composed of 61 different designs. Attached to the verso of each sheet is an historical resume of origin and date. All papers are printed "Waterfast Finish". The cover is bound with ivory colored paper simulating leather. Cover ornaments with rococo scroll printed in gilt.

tombstone.epitaph: Sidewall - Sample, Album of Authentic Reproductions of Famous Historical Wall Papers, 1946; Manufactured by M.H. Birge & Sons Co. (United States); USA; machine-printed on paper; 52 x 46.5 cm (20 1/2 x 18 5/16 in.); 1947-35-1-1/162
